            <span class="block text-white mt-3">Presentation Is Professional</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">{description}</p>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border-[3px] border-white/30 p-6 rounded-lg">
