            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-red-400 font-black text-2xl flex-shrink-0">✗</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-white text-lg">Heavy 3MB photos = PageSpeed 48 = 67% bounce rate</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1">Gorgeous 3MB photos. PageSpeed 48. Mobile load: 12 seconds. Bounce rate 67%. Beautiful photos that don't load = no photos at all. Compress to 200KB, lazy loading, proper sizing. PageSpeed 96, mobile load 2 seconds, bounce 23%. Mobile is 67% of traffic. Optimize or lose.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

